<html>
  <head>
    <style>
      :root {
        color-scheme: light;
        supported-color-schemes: light;
      }

      body {
        font-family: Verdana, sans-serif;
        font-size: 0.8em;
        color: #484848;
        background: #FFFFFF;
        margin: 0;
        padding: 0;
      }

      @media (prefers-color-scheme: dark) {
        body {
          color: #484848 !important;
          background: #FFFFFF !important;
        }
      }

      .container {
        text-align: center;
        background-color: #f5f5f5;
        color: white;
        padding-bottom: 20px;
      }

      .header {
        background-color: #003575;
        padding: 10px 0px;
        font-size: 1.25rem;
        display: inline-block;
        align-items: center;
		    width:100%
      }

      .content {
        text-align: left;
        background-color: #ffffff;
        border-radius: 10px;
        margin: 20px auto;
        max-width: 650px;
        border: 1px solid #f0f0f0;
        padding: 20px;
        color: #303030;
      }

      .footer {
        font-size: 0.8em;
        font-style: italic;
        border-top-width: 1px;
        border-top-color: #ccc;
        border-top-style: solid;
        text-align: center;
        padding-top: 10px;
      }

      .footer-note {
        border-top: 1px solid #eeeeee;
        padding-top: 20px;
        margin-top: 20px !important;
        color: #777777;
        text-align: justify;
      }

      .title {
        margin-top: 10px;
        margin-bottom: 20px;
        text-align: center;
      }

      .copyright {
        margin-bottom: 10px;
        color: #777777;
      }

      .logo {
        height: 30px;
        width: auto;
        vertical-align: middle;

      }

      .system-title {
        text-align: center;
        color: #ffffff;
        vertical-align: middle;

      }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body>
    <div class="container">
      <div class="header">
        <%= image_tag(attachments['aoz_logo.png'].url, alt: 'AlphaOmegaZed', class:"logo") %>

        <div class="system-title">
          Project Management
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="content">
        <% if title %>
          <h2 class="title"><%= title %></h2>
        <% end %>

        <%= yield %>

        <div class="footer-note">
          Αυτό είναι ένα αυτοματοποιημένο μήνυμα. Παρακαλούμε μην απαντήσετε σε αυτό το μήνυμα ηλεκτρονικού ταχυδρομείου.
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- <div class="copyright">
        © Alpha Omega Zed Project Management
      </div> -->
    </div>
  </body>
</html>
